sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh (mm)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>(model server)
    participant PredCtrl as Predictor Controller
    participant SRCtrl as ServingRuntime Controller
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as Object Storage (S3)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>MM: gRPC inference request<br/>:8033/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
        MM->>Runtime: Route to loaded model<br/>UDS or localhost gRPC
        Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
        MM-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: REST Inference Request (via OAuth)
        Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>:8443/TCP TLS, OAuth Bearer Token
        OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate token (OpenShift SAR check)
        OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: Forward HTTP request<br/>:8008/TCP (pod-internal)
        RESTProxy->>MM: Translate HTTP to gRPC<br/>:8033/TCP (pod-internal)
        MM->>Runtime: Route to loaded model<br/>UDS or localhost gRPC
        Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
        MM-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
        OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over PredCtrl,S3: Flow 3: Model Registration and Loading
        PredCtrl->>MM: gRPC registerModel / setVModel<br/>:8033/TCP, Optional TLS
        MM->>etcd: Store vmodel state<br/>:2379/TCP gRPC, Optional TLS/mTLS<br/>Auth: username/password
        MM->>Puller: Request model download<br/>:8086/TCP gRPC (pod-internal)
        Puller->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>:443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: access key/secret
        S3-->>Puller: Model artifacts
        Puller-->>MM: Model ready
        MM->>Runtime: Load model
        Runtime-->>MM: Model loaded
        MM->>etcd: Update model state to LOADED
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over SRCtrl,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Scale-to-Zero and Autoscaling
        SRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Watch/Update Deployment replicas<br/>:443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        SRCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create/Delete HPA<br/>:443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        PredCtrl->>etcd: Watch ModelMeshEventStream<br/>:2379/TCP gRPC<br/>Auth: username/password
        etcd-->>PredCtrl: Model state change events
        Note over SRCtrl: Grace period (default 60s)<br/>then scale to 0 replicas<br/>and delete HPA
    end
